    <h1>Natkra Commission Info</h1>
    <h1>Prices & TOS</h1>

    <p>Please make yourself familiar with all the information below before asking for a commission! :)</p>
    <p>I am 19, at university, and I have a job , so please have patience if I take a while to respond at first. I will only start a commission when I know I have time :) </p>
    <p>I live in the UK (BST). </p>

    <hr>

    <p><strong>Interested?</strong><br>
        Message me on discord at <em>‘arktanz’</em><br>
        <strong>Commissions are always open, however I don't take on many at a time. Message me on discord to check my availability :)</strong> </p>

    <p>Average commission time is: <br>
        7 - 14 days(ish) for lineart <br>
        5 - 7 days(ish) for colouring and shading. </p>
    <p>Please allow up to three weeks in total from start to finish :) I have a part time job and I go to university to please be patient if it takes a while. I’ll always put commissions as a higher priority in the later stage once you’ve paid for it.</p>

    <hr>

    <p>My commissions cost the same for half body view, ¾ view and full bodys. </p>

    <br><br/>

    <p>1. I will begin working on a commission as soon as I can. I will then make simple and rough lineart, which I will send to you with a <strong>watermark</strong>.</p>
    <p>2. You can then ask for any changes you would like, as long as they <strong>aren't too drastic</strong> (e.g completely different pose). <strong>Payment isn’t required</strong> until after you’re happy with your lineart.</p>
    <p>3. Once payment is complete, I will send over the <strong>un-watermarked lineart</strong> and I will finish the artwork.</p>
    <p>4. Once I've finished you can then ask for any more slight changes to do with colouring or shading, or any other final touches.</p>

    <br><br/>

    <p>Payment is by <strong>PayPal invoice</strong> only, so I’ll need your email address when it comes to this stage. I’ll always let you know how much it’ll be before starting :)</p>

    <p>Please know what you want before you ask for a commission! I unfortunately suck at coming up with ideas so I can’t help you.</p>
    <p>I can refuse any commission for any reason. </p>
    <p>There are <strong>No refunds</strong> once you’ve sent payment.</p>

