    <p class="price">£25 GBP</p>
    <p>A full drawing of your character of choice. I’ll shade and colour simply, with a thick outline to show depth. I’ll also do a simple background if you like, or you could have a transparent png background. </p>

    <img src="art/commissionart/Untitled-2.png" alt="Simple Shading Example 1">

