    <p class="price">£35 GBP</p>
    <p>Full character drawing in any pose you like. I’ll spend a lot of time on the shading and colouring, also with a simple background if you’d like. </p>

    <img src="art/commissionart/Untitled-3.png" alt="Complex Shading Example 1">


    <p>For all tiers, each extra character adds on 50% of the original commission price. <br>
        For example: 1 character is £35 <br>
        2 characters are £35 + (£35*0.5) = £52.50 <br>
        3 characters are £52.50 + (£35*0.5) = £69.75 </p>

