    <h2>Posting, sharing and editing</h2>
    <p>If you get a commission from me, you can:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Post and share it wherever you like.</li>
        <li>Crop, edit, trace, redraw, or change the artwork any way you want.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>The only things you <strong>can’t do</strong> are: <strong>use it commercially</strong> to make money, or <strong>pretend you drew it yourself</strong>.</p>
    <p>If you post it, please either: credit me as the artist, or make sure that my signature is visible in the image :))</p>

